Instruction for Cursor AI:

Always use design_tokens.tokens.json as the Source of Truth for all styling, colors, and spacing.

Follow the 8pt Grid System for all margins and padding (using spacing_xs to spacing_xl).

Use Pretendard for all Korean text to maintain a professional look.

Home Tab Logic: Apply ui_state_locked (30% opacity) for locked lessons and ui_state_primed (50% opacity) for lessons where the quiz is done but the call is pending.

Ranking Tab Logic: Use the color_rank palette for user badges and highlight the "Promotion Zone" (Top 10) with ui_state_promotion_zone.